    <p>Size mat­ters in more ways than one to the 8-se­ries Gran Coupe, BMW’s new four-door tourer. Its dimensions make it big­ger than its keen­est ri­vals. In its class, the car’s med­ley of glass, ve­neer and leather is sec­ond to none. It has the lat­est tech, with the nifti­est be­ing an adap­tive cruise con­trol.</p>


